  <h1><span>April 25, 1980: Statement on the Iran Rescue Mission</span>
</h1>


    <div class="share-trigger-mobile"></div>
</div>
<div id="block-mainpagecontent">
  
    
      <article role="article" class="presidential-speech">

  
    

  <div class="ps-container video-container">
    <div class="presidential-speeches--sidebar">
      
<div  class="about-this-episode">
    <h3>About this speech</h3>
      
<div  class="about-this-episode--inner">
      
            <p class="president-name">Jimmy Carter</p>
      
            <p class="episode-date">April 25, 1980</p>
      
  <div class="speech-location-container">
    <span class="speech-label">Location</span>
              <span class="speech-loc">National Archives</span>
          </div>

            <div class="about-sidebar--intro"><p>On the subject of the Iran Hostage Affair, Carter informs the nation of the failed attempt to rescue the American hostages, via military means.</p>
</div>
      
  </div>
  </div>
    </div>

    <div class="presidential-speeches--body-wrapper">
     <a href="/the-presidency/presidential-speeches" class="back-to-listing--cta">Presidential Speeches</a> <span class="nav-separator">|</span> <label class="presidential-speeches--label">Jimmy Carter Presidency</label>
      <h2 class="presidential-speeches--title"><span>April 25, 1980: Statement on the Iran Rescue Mission</span>
</h2>
      
<div  class="presidential-speeches--body">
      <div class="video-parent">
	<div class="video-container">
	<video  poster=https://millercenter.org/sites/default/files/styles/video_poster_16x9_desktop_2x/public/mc-logo-video-poster.jpg?itok=FzwnVIyd controls>
	    <source type="video/mp4" src="https://web2.millercenter.org/speeches/video/mp4/1Mb/spe_1980_0425_carter.mp4">
	</video>
	<div class="poster-frame">
	    
            <div class="article--teaser-image-field">  <img src="/sites/default/files/styles/video_poster_16x9_desktop_2x/public/mc-logo-video-poster.jpg?itok=FzwnVIyd" width="1600" height="900" alt="Miller Center logo" />


</div>
      
	    <a href="https://web2.millercenter.org/speeches/video/mp4/1Mb/spe_1980_0425_carter.mp4" class="video-trigger">Play Video</a>
	</div>
